title: Focused Haidian area 'fully mature' after 2 years' development (Beijing Municipal Government)
text: ( Source : Beijing Municipal Government ) A focused intellectual property area in Beijing is fully mature after about two year's development and aims to be a site where IP is well respected and used, said Wang Ying , IP chief in Haidian
